tptSmsQuarantineRequest.name: tptSmsQuarantineRequest
tptSmsQuarantineRequest.description: SMS asking an external NMS to quarantine an endstation using the data embedded in the request

tptSmsQuarantineAck.name: tptSmsQuarantineAck
tptSmsQuarantineAck.description: External NMS notifying the SMS that a previously quarantine request was processed.

tptSmsQuarantineReleaseRequest.name: tptSmsQuarantineReleaseRequest
tptSmsQuarantineReleaseRequest.description: SMS asking an external NMS to unquarantine an endstation using the data embedded in the request

tptSmsQuarantineReleaseAck.name: tptSmsQuarantineReleaseAck
tptSmsQuarantineReleaseAck.description: External NMS notifying the SMS that a previously unquarantine request was processed.

tptSmsQuarantinePolicyNotification.name: tptSmsQuarantinePolicyNotification
tptSmsQuarantinePolicyNotification.description: SMS sending notification of a policy match

tptSmsUnQuarantineRequest.name: tptSmsUnQuarantineRequest
tptSmsUnQuarantineRequest.description: Inverse of tptSMSQuarantineCommand - command the SMS to unquarantine an endstation. You can explicitly specify a quarantined host ID if you know it; otherwise, you may specify the IP only, in which case the SMS will look up the MAC; or the IP+MAC.

tptSmsQuarantineCommand.name: tptSmsQuarantineCommand
tptSmsQuarantineCommand.description: Inverse of tptSmsUnquarantineRequest Command the SMS to quarantine an endstation. SMS will look up the MAC.

tptSmsRepDvVerifySuccess.name: tptSmsRepDvVerifySuccess
tptSmsRepDvVerifySuccess.description: SMS: Reputation DV downloaded and verified.

tptSmsRepDvVerifyFail.name: tptSmsRepDvVerifyFail
tptSmsRepDvVerifyFail.description: SMS: Reputation DV downloaded. Verification failed.

tptDeviceNonComm.name: tptDeviceNonComm
tptDeviceNonComm.description: SMS has lost communications with a device.

tptSmsQuarantineNotifyId.name: tptSmsQuarantineNotifyId
tptSmsQuarantineNotifyId.description: A unique incrementing integer assigned for each quarantine event.

tptSmsQuarantineNotifyData.name: tptSmsQuarantineNotifyData
tptSmsQuarantineNotifyData.description: A string consisting of the parameters used to identify the device to quarantine. The format is NAME:VALUE with multiple parameters separated by a newline

tptSmsQuarantinePolicyMatchData.name: tptSmsQuarantinePolicyMatchData
tptSmsQuarantinePolicyMatchData.description: A string consisting of the parameters used to identify the matching policy

tptSmsQuarantineNotifyType.name: tptSmsQuarantineNotifyType
tptSmsQuarantineNotifyType.description: A string consisting of the parameters used to identify the matching policy

tptSmsQuarantineDeviceIP.name: tptSmsQuarantineDeviceIP
tptSmsQuarantineDeviceIP.description: An IP address used as a trap parameter.

tptSmsQuarantineDeviceMAC.name: tptSmsQuarantineDeviceMAC
tptSmsQuarantineDeviceMAC.description: A MAC address used a a trap parameter

tptSmsQuarantineSwitchPort.name: tptSmsQuarantineSwitchPort
tptSmsQuarantineSwitchPort.description: A port number or index used as a trap parameter

tptSmsQuarantineEndpointUser.name: tptSmsQuarantineEndpointUser
tptSmsQuarantineEndpointUser.description: A string consisting of the parameters used to identify the matching policy

tptSmsQuarantineNotifyActionList.name: tptSmsQuarantineNotifyActionList
tptSmsQuarantineNotifyActionList.description: A string consisting of the parameters used to identify the matching policy

tptSmsQuarantineNotifyParamList.name: tptSmsQuarantineNotifyParamList
tptSmsQuarantineNotifyParamList.description: A string consisting of the parameters used to identify the matching policy

tptSmsQuarantineNotifyOptionList.name: tptSmsQuarantineNotifyOptionList
tptSmsQuarantineNotifyOptionList.description: A string consisting of the parameters used to identify the matching policy

tptSmsQuarantinePolicyName.name: tptSmsQuarantinePolicyName
tptSmsQuarantinePolicyName.description: The name of an SMS Quarantine Policy. If the named policy does not exists on the SMS, a default will be chosen.

tptSmsQuarantineDataGroup.name: tptSmsQuarantineDataGroup
tptSmsQuarantineDataGroup.description: Payload of SMS quarantine traps consisting of a unique identifier and a parseable string

tptSmsQuarantineNotifyGroup.name: tptSmsQuarantineNotifyGroup
tptSmsQuarantineNotifyGroup.description: SMS quarantine traps sent to an NMS to indicate devices that require a quarantine operation

tptSmsQuarantineNotifyAckGroup.name: tptSmsQuarantineNotifyAckGroup
tptSmsQuarantineNotifyAckGroup.description: SMS quarantine traps sent to an SMS system to indicate devices that have been quarantined

tptSmsQuarantineRequestGroup.name: tptSmsQuarantineRequestGroup
tptSmsQuarantineRequestGroup.description: SMS quarantine traps received to indicate devices that require a (un)quarantine operation
